{"tid":757232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我老母咁樣關心令我更加痛苦","createTime":"2018-07-26T16:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T10:02:01.000Z","uid":72453,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d244d29aa32f151e41a9310c89e35c21a6af35e2","tid":757232,"uid":72453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:02:12.000Z","msg":"自己無料，打份萬二蚊工，人工係唔高，但都夠使，自己都覺得ok總會慢慢升<br />\n<br />\n我老母就成日講，你呢行人工係低架啦，唔緊要啦，人工低係咁架啦之類，明明本身都唔覺萬二蚊有咩問題，俾佢講完我就覺得好似人工好撚低咁，明明無密嘢變到好撚sad<br />\n<br />\n然後今個月有津貼出咗萬五蚊糧，比兩千五家用，佢就講笑咁同我講 你出萬五蚊唔係俾咁少阿？仲以為自己好風趣咁，知唔知我個心好撚痛哭<br />\n定係真係比得太少<br />\n<br />\n上個月出萬二蚊 俾二千家用佢反而唔要，話有淨先俾，我好亂就嚟癲<br />\n<br />\n我真係因爲佢講嘅嘢覺得自己廢上加廢<br />\n講幾句好聽嘅都咁撚難？"},{"pid":"25e69d417606fbc3197282608ecdcd7c6a0237ac","tid":757232,"uid":53923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:10:15.000Z","msg":"我呀媽都係唔識表達<br />\n雖然知係關心緊我<br />\n但啲說話令我更反感更唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1458664c76afc39007ce5be69661640d4e6da8c","tid":757232,"uid":152676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:11:22.000Z","msg":"咩行業"},{"pid":"a61a7d422e03c69124739040a0c9884000d47216","tid":757232,"uid":46911,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:11:59.000Z","msg":"搵萬五比二千又真係少左啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0e2f71b523723ddee05c2b8721cc06ca956d7f","tid":757232,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a61a7d422e03c69124739040a0c9884000d47216","tid":757232,"uid":46911,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:11:59.000Z","msg":"搵萬五比二千又真係少左啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:14:18.000Z","msg":"唔只二千&hellip;<br />\n係二千五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aebd83091fa0a89dd160d6b0c69f7ef22c802dd","tid":757232,"uid":164885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"